## 1. PURPOSE

This project, "Bookstore Application - Java EE 8 Learning Project," is created for **educational purposes only** as part of:

- **Bundeswehr-Lehrgang 8606:** "Java f√ºr Fortgeschrittene Teil 2" (Java for Advanced Users Part 2)
- **Reference Material:** "Professionell entwickeln mit Java EE 8" by Alexander Salvanos (Rheinwerk Verlag)

The project serves as a **learning template** and **practical reference** for Java EE 8 development.

